==================
Apache
sudo a2enmod dump_io
a2enmod dump_io

open apache2.conf
# enable this if you just want to capture http request
DumpIOInput On
# enable this if you just want to capture http response
DumpIOOutput On
# capture everything
DumpIOLogLevel debug

$ sudo /etc/init.d/apache2 restart 

